synonym: "Charlevoix disease" EXACT [DOID:0090003, icd11.foundation:1443432032, OMIM:218000, Orphanet:1496]
synonym: "corpus callosum agenesis neuronopathy" RELATED [GARD:0001537]
synonym: "corpus callosum agenesis-neuronopathy syndrome" EXACT [DOID:0090003, Orphanet:1496]
synonym: "corpus callosum, agenesis of, with neuronopathy" RELATED []
synonym: "hereditary motor and sensory neuropathy with agenesis of the corpus callosum" EXACT [MONDO:0009023]
synonym: "HMSN/ACC" RELATED [GARD:0001537]
synonym: "peripheral neuropathy associated with agenesis of the corpus callosum" EXACT []
synonym: "polyneuropathy, sensorimotor, with or without agenesis of the corpus callosum" RELATED []
