[Term]
id: MONDO:0000903
name: myoclonus-dystonia syndrome
def: "Myoclonus-dystonia syndrome (MDS) is a rare movement disorder characterized by mild to moderate dystonia along with 'lightning-like' myoclonic jerks." [Orphanet:36899]
