synonym: "chronic relapsing polyneuropathy" EXACT [https://rarediseases.org/rare-diseases/chronic-inflammatory-demyelinating-polyneuropathy/]
synonym: "CIDP" EXACT ABBREVIATION [https://rarediseases.org/rare-diseases/chronic-inflammatory-demyelinating-polyneuropathy/, NCIT:C84636, Orphanet:2932]
