synonym: "PCWH" EXACT ABBREVIATION [DOID:0090111, MONDO:Lexical, OMIM:609136, Orphanet:163746]
synonym: "peripheral demyelinating neuropathy, central dysmyelination, Waardenburg syndrome, and Hirschsprung disease" EXACT [DOID:0090111, MONDO:Lexical, OMIM:609136]
synonym: "peripheral demyelinating neuropathy-central dysmyelinating leukodystrophy-Hirschsprung disease-Waardenburg syndrome" EXACT [DOID:0090111]
synonym: "peripheral demyelinating neuropathy-central dysmyelinating leukodystrophy-Waardenburg syndrome-Hirschsprung disease" RELATED []
synonym: "Waardenburg-Shah syndrome, neurologic variant" RELATED []
synonym: "WS4 plus" EXACT [Orphanet:163746]
